title: Singer Navi returns after five months with 'Please Call' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Singer Navi returns after five months with 'Please Call' By KpopJoA 27 minutes ago 1,045 100 0 0 Google+ Singer Navi came back after five months with a new song " Please Call "!
"Please Call" is a heartfelt ballad that illustrates the emotions of opening up to a loved one, and emphasizes the importance of communication. Not much had been revealed prior to the release, except with Navi commenting on her SNS page 'D-1 ' on February 14 with a photo. 
Check out the song above!
